Product name: itWorks(tm) ANTI-PERSPIRANT Deodorant, Normal and Sensitive Skin (baking soda free)--Organic
Description:
No, this is not a trick, nor an oxymoron.
We've tested it, incorporating latest research, and are pleased to present a natural solution for heavy perspiration.  There is no aluminum or other heavy metals present in this formula.  The specific blend of essential oils works to gradually and naturally reduce sweating in most individuals.  New users will experience a period of adjustment ranging from 2 days to 2 weeks, after which time you can fully judge how a particular blend performs on you.  If you experience body odor in the morning, use the deodorant at night to speed up the process of adjustment.
The additional aromas (described below) are not simply fragrances, but additional essential oil blends with slightly different affect on individual body chemistry.  Most of our essential oils are organic and we use a complex blend of 13 base essential oils to keep you clean, healthy, and smelling great!
Our deodorants and antiperspirants are made with organic coconut oil for its antibacterial and anti fungal properties, organic butters that nourish and moisturize underarms, and arrowroot powder that absorbs moisture and draws toxins out of your skin. We don't use corn starch, which, while absorbing sweat, also feeds the underarm bacteria!
There are two types of antiperspirant offered, REGULAR formula and SENSITIVE (without baking soda).  The sensitivity does not correspond to otherwise "sensitive" skin, but only to sensitivity to baking soda, which you may or may not have. If you have previously determined sensitivity to baking soda, order the sensitive formula. If you are using the normal formula and develop underarm irritation, itchiness, or redness, you are likely sensitive to baking soda and should switch from the normal to the sensitive formula.  You can TEST yourself for SENSITIVITY to baking soda by applying a wet paste made with water and baking soda to your underarms.  If you have no reaction to the baking soda past, you should be fine with the normal formula.
The degree of sensitivity varies from person to person.
---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
SUMMER FORMULA is a default March 15 until September 15.
WINTER FORMULA is default September 16 until March 14.
If you prefer a softer, creamier formula, live in a cold climate, or your house temperature is below 72F at night, please ask for a WINTER formula. Summer formula is for indoor (bathroom) temperatures that exceed 72-74F at night or for carrying around in heat (beach, gym bags, purses, etc...).If asking for a formula that is not the current default, please indicate your choice with at NOTE AT CHECKOUT.  
------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
INTERNATIONAL ORDERS: Due to rate changes by United States Postal Service it is now much more cost effective to ship MULTIPLE tubes of deodorant.  With new rates, 1 tube costs us about 14 in shipping, whereas 2-7 tubes can be shipped for 22.
_________________________________________________________________________
The essential oil aroma choices are arranged in a descending order of body odor control strength, starting with the strongest blend.  For comparison, Tom's of Maine scented deodorants are about strength 2-3, and Lavanila strength 3-4.
AROMAS: 
FIR FOREST:  This scent has a top note of Douglas Fir (it smells like a Christmas Tree!!), embedded in a blend that includes warm and classy sandalwood, spicy cedar wood and lemon, and undertones of patchouli and coconut.  This scent combination lasts the longest and is the original itWorks! formulation. It is suitable for men and women. Strongest protection (strength 10)!  This formula is recommended for hormonal and stress induced sweating as well as hyperhydrosis.
WARM SPICE: This is a wonderful blend of cinnamon, clove, orange and other warm aromas that remind you of fall harvest or winter holidays (or a holiday pie fresh out of the oven!).  As a side benefit, all of these essential oils also have strong deodorizing properties.  This deodorant can be requested "in brown" (no white marks!!) with the addition of pure organic cinnamon powder, which keeps you even drier and smelling even better!  You must request it brown, or it will be made without the additional cinnamon powder. (strength 9)
ROSE GERANIUM: A beautiful blend that harnesses all the best of Geranium, without the excessive and heady floral overtones.  It is revitalizing (particularly to women), detoxifying, and regenerative.  It's astringent properties are also useful in the deodorant blend, as is its effect on Candida. (Strength 9)
BOUQUET:  This combination of essential oils features a slightly green top note of delicate white flowers, including rose, neroli, geranium, bee balm, and violet. The scent mellows out into a classy light floral aroma. (Strength 7)
MYSTIC MANDARIN: Is likewise a citrus blend, but with more punch and spice than Sweet Orange Vanilla itWorks! Natural Deodorant.  It smells very loemon-y, very close to Lemon Verbena. It does not smell like Tangarines (mandarines): it is a blend of Neroli, Bergamot and May Chang as the top note.  Really stimulating and suitable for men and women.  May Chang has additional benefits of strong anti-microbial and cooling properties. May Chang's molecular constituents have been shown effective in inducing death and halting proliferation of non-small cell lung cancer. Peer-reviewed PLoS One journal (10/12/2012) published a study titled: "Vapor of volatile oils from Litsea cubeba seed induces apoptosis and causes cell cycle arrest in lung cancer cells." Researchers seperated four individual compounds from the 'crude' essential oil, and tested each for their cytotoxic properties on cancerous cells. Three of the four compounds showed cyctotoxic properties, resulting in cancer cell death. Importantly, these compounds at the concentrations tested did not adversely affect healthy lung cells in any way. Further, it was noted that a combination of the components was more effective that any single constituent. This supports the aroma-therapeutic principal that a whole, natural essential oil will be the best choice for virtually any given health-supporting application.  The study also noted that the benefits of May Chang can be delivered purely through inhalation! (Strength 6)
MEN'S CLASSIC: This formula is based on the most popular men's cologne ingredients, including petitgrain, rosemary, atlas cedar, calendula and rock rose.  It does not smell like petitgrain, but like a complex blend that it is. (Strength 6)
SPRING BREEZE:  If you have endured a long and cold winter, then you will appreciate the fabulous aroma of an evening garden in the spring and its wafting fragrance. This scent starts of with a sweet floral note and ages to a slightly floral baby powder type aroma. As always, only pure therapeutic-grade essential oils are used to blend into a wonderful, refreshing scent of our newest addition. (Strength 5)
LEMON VERBENA: BACK IN STOCK!
The most refreshing and sophisticated single note aroma. period.  This is a bestseller with good reason. Since Lemon Verbena can be sun sensitizing and we don't use it in creams and lotions, this is a great way to enjoy its benefits and aroma. There is currently a shortage of pure Lemon Verbena essential oil on the world market, so we may run out before new supplies become available. (Strength 5)
----------------------------------------------------------------------------------
RECENT FEEDBACK:
"Love, love, love it!! It REALLY DOES WORK! Kept me dry in HK (mid-high 80's, 70-80% humidity) & in HI (mid 70's - mid 80's, 60-70% humidity)!! Haven't been able to use commercial antiperspirants for 30 years!! With these antiperspirants I had no rash, no burning & no itching!! Kept me dry for more than 24 hrs!! Will be ordering full size now that I used up the trial sizes! Fast shipping! Aleksandra is a GENIUS! She is also patient to answer & explain all your questions! NO commercial "natural" antiperspirant comes close to this! I have tried them all & this is the ONLY one I can use!!! I have extremely sensitive skin. I like the deodorants but I absolutely LOVE being DRY INSTEAD!! I am so thankful I came across this antiperspirant!! Thank you very, very much Aleksandra!!!"
"I usually don't buy natural deodorant because I sweat a lot and need something stronger like an antiperspirant. I've been using a top brand antiperspirant filled with chemicals and aluminum for years, even though all my other personal care products are strictly natural & organic when possible. Truly natural antiperspirants are hard to come by and deodorants don't help with the wetness. So, you could imagine my surprise when I came across this antiperspirant! First of all, it smells AMAZING and leaves NO white marks!! It's great after shaving and is completely natural, but the best part is that it works like a chemical antiperspirant!! I wore this on a hot summer day (80 degrees) and I was still feeling dry and had no odor by the day's end! Honestly, I have officially switched to this antiperspirant and will be upgrading to the full-size after I finish the trial. I'm really glad I came across this product! Thanks SO much Aleksandra!!! :)"
"I think we have a winner! I have purchased other natural deodorants to find after a couple days time, my armpit has turned red. I purchased the sensitive formula and after 4 days now I am still fine. The Rose Geranium scent is lovely as well and I find do have any foul odor. Thanks and I'll be back!"
"I've been using bodyBrana itWorks deodorant with sage for the past month and its awesome! Just a little goes a long way. I smell absolutely NO odor, not even a hint. Its not like a standard liquid roll-on or stick variety, its a thick all-natural creamy deo stick. A blend of organic cocoa butter, natural vegetable powders and clays, baking soda and essential oils neutralize odor for hours and hours (in my case it lasts all day). Make sure it dries before you dress up. You can get custom made deo with your choice of fragrance! With many natural deodorants, they are okay and semi-effective and I've used many where I have to re-apply throughout the day and if you're sweating like crazy, deodorant doesn't usually help with the wetness factor. This is taking care of both issues, due to sage and arrow root powder in it. I can not wait to put this to the test in the middle of summer!"
Works really well in this Florida heat. Like the personal note too."
"...Just how great your product is!!! And how much I love it!
I mean I've had seriously sensitive skin the whole of my life.
Many times if I try a new lotion, soap, laundry detergent, etc. I end up so itchy that I have to take a shower immediately. So when I find something that works well.... it's just like a miracle for me.
I have tried 2 other good for avoidance of breast cancer deodorants. Neither of them worked as deodorants. And one of them gave me a rash.
So finding yours is just amazing for me and I am very grateful!"

Natural Antiperspirant (Net Wt 3 oz): This pure and natural anti-perspirant builds on the great formula of the natural deodorant (see the description here: 
https://www.etsy.com/listing/113102964/itworks-natural-deodorant
 ), but modifies ingredient proportions and also includes a synergistic combination of essential oils including elemi and sage, both proven to reduce sweating.  
Unlike the heavy-metal drugstore formulas (based on aluminum), this deodorant does NOT block your pores and lock in the toxins that would otherwise be naturally excreted from your body, but it reduces most of the heavy sweating from the inside out. Product name: Natural loose linen pants / Washed women linen trousers / Slightly tapered linen pants
Description:
Washed and soft natural linen pants for simple and casual look. Pants have elastic waistband. 

WHAT MAKES YOUR ITEM SPECIAL 
Our items are handmade in small studio in small quantities of washed linen fabric, specially woven for us by our local linen manufacturers. The procedure of making these items takes time and effort, cause the items are double washed once they are made. Only after such process we reach extra softness and natural wrinkles.

DESCRIPTION:
- made from 100 % European linen (flax) - medium weight linen.
- the model is 172 cm high (regular XS) and the model is wearing size XS.
- two deep pockets,
- elastic waistband and drawstring (for dark color pants we will choose the  drawstring to be dark, for light colors it will be natural and undyed, but if you want any other choices, please leave a note); You can always take the drawstring of the pants if you want more official look; 
- color in the picture - natural. Please choose any other color on the right.
- not ironed (and no need to iron to have a relaxed look);
- handmade by small creative family.

THE FIT
The pants are rather roomy and slightly tapered being more wider in the hip area.
1.  We recommend to order your regular size for the fit like in the photos. They will be roomy and loose enough.
2. We recommend to order one size smaller for more fitted look. The customers who wanted more fitted look and ordered one size smaller were happy with the fit.   

COLOR
Natural color linen fabric may vary in every roll - as it is not dyed it depends on the flax itself (how it was grown, dried  etc.) and sometimes have darker or lighter shade.   
We found out linen to be rather hard to photograph to have an exact color for exposure - linen wrinkles often catches unexpected light and show thousands of shades in different positions and certain lights. The actual colors also vary due to your computer resolution and monitor color restrictions.
If you doubt about the color, we always suggest to have FABRIC SAMPLES to be send to you first before purchasing the exact item. The listing of the fabric samples can be found here:
https://www.etsy.com/listing/483583193/fabric-samples?ref=shop_home_active_1
If you are already purchasing any other item at the time (making an order), you may not order samples as they will be included in your package anyway.
